1. ## **Alien Worlds**:

Genre: NFT Trading Card

Token: Trillium ($TLM)

Play Options: Play-to-earn and Free-to-play

Overview:

![][image1]  
[Source](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*RCxjefiHrEwH3T-O47XVHQ.png)

Alien Worlds is a Web3 game where players compete for rare assets in a stimulated economy centered around planetary worlds. The game uses non-fungible tokens (NFTs) as a means of exchange and allows players to earn real-world money through gameplay or participation in Planet Decentralized Autonomous Organizations (DAOs).

In Alien Worlds, players are called "explorers" and can earn in-game currency, Trilium (TLM), by mining. They can also earn NFT packs or battle with other users for NFTs. To boost their rewards, players can stake $TLM or use it to vote in the Planet DAOs.

Alien Worlds has gained popularity as a play-to-earn (P2E) NFT game, The game has established a roadmap, including being listed on Binance launchpad, a farming period of $TLM on Binance Launchpool, and the development of various game features.

Alien Worlds also has a unique gaming metaverse that incorporates decentralized autonomous organizations (DAOs) into gameplay. $TLM coin holders can use their coins to stake, vote, or even become a leader in the platform, making the decision-making process more democratic. Players can stake their $TLM to Planet DAOs, which shows their allegiance to a planet and earns them more daily TLM rewards.

Another feature of Alien Worlds is that it is free-to-play, removing the barrier to entry for many traditional games that require expensive upfront costs. This makes it more accessible and appealing to new players.

The platform also allows players to run for candidacy to become a Councillor in multiple planets. Each planet can have more than one elected Councillor who shares multisig control over the Planet DAO account, further empowering the community to shape the platform's future.

Alien Worlds has gained immense popularity, ranking first in all DApp games by 24-hour users according to DappRadar. This success can be attributed to the team's community development efforts, which include active engagement in 18 languages on Discord and localization efforts to support Filipino, Indonesian, and Indian players. Other community efforts include onboarding popular intellectual properties, sponsoring drops and promotions, and conducting regular AMAs.

2. ## **XWorld games:**

Genre: NFT Trading card

Token: XWorld Game ($XWG)

Play Option: Play-to-earn and Free-to-play

Overview:  
![][image2]  
[source](https://110547582-files.gitbook.io/~/files/v0/b/gitbook-x-prod.appspot.com/o/spaces%2F-MXoNK4xcv0kyfjqFXN5-3008180417%2Fuploads%2FDaUszcc9lU0uK5k3bKfr%2F1627899561164.jpeg?alt=media&token=0bab3682-0d39-4d53-b20e-9532f05d6306)

X World Games is a Web3 gaming ecosystem that aims to simplify blockchain features and make NFT ownership fun and accessible for non-crypto players. The name X WorldGames combines "X World," which refers to an open virtual world where all players meet, and "Game," which encompasses all games available in the ecosystem that are connected to these open lands.

The game ecosystem is decentralized through a DAO, allowing players to create various in-game items such as unique avatars and fantasy equipment, all tokenized and represented by NFTs. These NFTs can be traded, providing players with ownership over their virtual assets.

The first gaming product released on the X World Games platform was "Dream Card," also known as "Dream Card V1." This game was inspired by the popular "Pokémon Trading Card Game" (TCG) and combines classic TCG battle functions and play styles with blockchain technology.

"Dream Card '' creates a play-to-earn ecosystem where players can earn rewards by playing the game and trading their NFTs.

The X World Games ecosystem aims to connect Web2 and Web3 gamers and help game developers enter the crypto space.

X World Games was founded in 2017 by a team with extensive experience in mobile gaming and the creation of online mini-games, with a track record that includes the wildly popular Japanese mobile game "Belle Battle Musou" with over a million active users.

The founder, Fernando, has a decade of investment expertise and a keen understanding of industry trends. His vision for a complete blockchain gaming ecosystem, which encompasses games, DeFi, NFTs, anime, metaverse, and more, was the driving force behind X World Games.

In 2019, the company launched its first NFT TCG game project, Dream Card, which drew inspiration from the Japanese ACG style. Following its Genesis Sale in 2021, X World Games released Dream Card v1 and v2, marking a significant milestone in the company's journey.

3. ## **Era7: Game of Truth:**

Genre: NFT Trading card

Token: Era7 ($ERA)

Play Option: Play-to-earn and Free-to-play

Overview:

![][image3]  
[Source](https://266050689-files.gitbook.io/~/files/v0/b/gitbook-x-prod.appspot.com/o/spaces%2FaYzDzakcM1qZpB1iGGYm%2Fuploads%2FRSvjUEErEQkZEZv9yjkE%2FThe%20Game%E2%80%99s%20Background.jpg?alt=media&token=6dd68e44-c1b7-424a-8bad-6ac59a4ea354)

Era7: Game of Truth is a Web3, metaverse-style trading card game (TCG) developed by a team of experienced blockchain technicians and game developers. The game offers an immersive and addictive gameplay experience that combines fighting and strategy, with each game session lasting for three minutes.

Players can collect cards of different rarities and combine them in various ways to create a strong deck. The game offers both player versus environment (PvE) and player versus player (PvP) modes.

Each card has unique effects that can be strategically deployed in battles. In addition to being fun to play, each card has a value that can be traded, summoned, or synthesized, making Era7 a GameFi project.

One of the biggest charms of Era7 is that it is constantly updated with new content, including new cards, playing methods, and battle passes. Early players of the game can earn dividends from the ecosystem, and there are reward mechanisms in place for inviting friends and sharing the game.

E-sports is also a core element of Era7, and players can use the game's competitive ecosystem to place bets. The game establishes an immersive gaming experience and a complete closed-loop economic system inside its metaverse, making it a unique and innovative gaming experience.

Overall, Era7: Game of Truth is a type of game that combines traditional TCG elements with the latest blockchain technology, creating an exciting and immersive gaming experience.

4. ## **Raini: The lords of light:**

Genre: NFT Trading card

Token: Raini ($RAINI)

Play Options: Play-to-earn and Free-to-play

Overview:  
![][image4]  
[Source](https://i.seadn.io/gae/blqzL-BgrSMxnDXejvsq4kDOcynNmrx2PgJXuzPvLyWPtpYq8c2HQWVDGSnNfYtLMQlA6jYaeMIXUQA1egoQiLgwDTTLYuMoweIeOQ?auto=format&w=1920)

“The Lords of Light'' is a trading card game that allows players to take on the role of a hero of one of the seven Lords of Light.

Players can command armies of mythological creatures and crypto legends to defeat other heroes and ultimately defeat the Quantum Rug.

The game incorporates a play-and-earn model, with players able to earn $RAINI tokens by winning battles, completing daily quests, winning tournaments, and renting out higher-level cards.

The game also has a rich lore set in the Rainiverse, where armies of mythological creatures engage in brutal battles driven by the will of the Seven Lords of Light.

Each Lord and card has a designated color. Lords, creatures, and weapons all imbued with a chance to trigger their respective color’s tribal ability whenever they attack an enemy creature.

The cards gain experience in ranked games and level up when they successfully attack and kill their opponents. As the level of difficulty increases, so does the value of the knowledge acquired by defeating stronger foes and through victories in games with higher ranks.

5. ## **Dracoo Master:**

Genre: NFT Trading card & MMORPG

Token: Dracoo Master ($DRA)

Play Options: Play-to-earn and Free-to-play

Overview:

![][image5]  
[Source](https://359721792-files.gitbook.io/~/files/v0/b/gitbook-x-prod.appspot.com/o/spaces%2Ft7JivR7ptPtEfzqOrVLI%2Fuploads%2F6mGRYjoDCokoI5GjBe8S%2FDracooWorld.png?alt=media&token=249a59b9-42c8-4347-875a-fec5e11ff35d)

Dracoo Master game is a strategic take on the trading card genre. Players can earn $DRA, an exclusive currency of the Dracoo World community, by participating in Adventure or Arena mode with a deck built using cards obtained from breeding Dracoos and using those cards to defeat other players. The platform also includes a map editor that allows users to freely alter and publish their own stages.

In Dracoo Master, you’ll engage in digital card duels using a deck-building mechanic. Each player takes a turn, limited to a maximum of 60 seconds. The game uses a unique set of cards with different functions, and players must use their Energy and Stamina Crystal points wisely to activate their cards and make strategic moves. The game includes three different modes: Adventure mode, Arena mode, and Guild War mode.

Overall, Dracoo World aims to be the most widely used Web3 social platform in the MMORPG industry. The platform's use of blockchain technology allows for fair and secure trading of virtual assets. With the addition of Dracoo Master, users have a variety of ways to engage with the platform and its community.
